        the formula used in the game is
            (1 - NumGoodsFactor * NumGoods) * (DistanceFactor * Distance)
        and lower values are deemed better.  Make sure that for a full out stock
        NumGoodsFactor * NumGoods < 1 or for a full stock distance will not
        matter (=0) or be deemed best (<0) which is highly dubious.  For
